    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.24) * v0) + ((tmp + 0.15 + tmp + 0.54) - (v0 + 0.00 - v2 + 0.65)))
    tmp = (0.99 * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.47) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.23)))
    v2 = (0.93 / v2)
